NAME: Residential Real Estate
DESCRIPTION: Residential real estate is a residence which is occupied by the owner or the lessee of the residence

NAME: Commercial Real Estate
DESCRIPTION: Commercial real estate is a real estate property where goods or services are provided to customers (e.g. hotels, restaurants, retail)

NAME: Industrial Real Estate
DESCRIPTION: Industrial real estate is real estate used for industrial purposes, such as those used as factories, logistical centres and storage space

NAME: Office Real Estate
DESCRIPTION: Office real estate is real estate used for business offices

NAME: Other Real Estate
DESCRIPTION: Other real estate is real estate other than residential, commercial, industrial and office real estate

NAME: Non Financial Asset Other Than Real Estate
DESCRIPTION: Non financial assets that is not real estate such as machinery and equipment, valuables, intellectual property products such as computer software and databases
